{"tid":2317463,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德州向最高法院控告喬治亞州，密歇根州，賓夕法尼亞州和威斯康星州選舉違規","createTime":"2020-12-08T14:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T15:12:50.000Z","uid":25468,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"edf1be47aaffa613f74151f250457882788251fb","tid":2317463,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T14:52:48.000Z","msg":"得薩斯州在周一向美國最高法院提起訴訟，對喬治亞州，密歇根州，賓夕法尼亞州和威斯康星州的選舉程序提出異議，理由是它們違反了憲法。<br />\n<br />\n德薩斯州稱這些州違反了《憲法》的選舉人條款，因為它們通過法院或行政措施（而非州立法機關）更改了投票規則和程序。此外，德克薩斯州辯稱，各州之間不同縣的投票規則和程序存在差異，這違反了憲法的平等保護條款。最後，得克薩斯州認為，由於上述原因，這些州存在&ldquo;投票違規行為&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.breitbart.com/politics/2020/12/07/texas-sues-georgia-michigan-pennsylvania-and-wisconsin-at-supreme-court-election-rules/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.breitbart.com%2Fpolitics%2F2020%2F12%2F07%2Ftexas-sues-georgia-michigan-pennsylvania-and-wisconsin-at-supreme-court-election-rules%2F&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W69osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=0692a77f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.breitbart.com/politics/2020/12/07/texas-sues-georgia-michigan-pennsylvania-and-wisconsin-at-supreme-court-election-rules/</a>"},{"pid":"017b8992e3cbf0c33ff1885b431e2a02360ef4cd","tid":2317463,"uid":64874,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T14:54:53.000Z","msg":"州可以告州，咁好明顯要聯邦法院處理"},{"pid":"b16f2e492302eac5c9189f1d6fe51428da62ef6d","tid":2317463,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"017b8992e3cbf0c33ff1885b431e2a02360ef4cd","tid":2317463,"uid":64874,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T14:54:53.000Z","msg":"州可以告州，咁好明顯要聯邦法院處理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T14:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"124a2c26e3d59121ced5f5416b8505b482a791fe","tid":2317463,"uid":38962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/231714